|   |-- label
|       |-- 1_sar_2.txt     eg. 1_2.tif 1_sar_2.tif 196 28
|   |-- img_list_path.txt
eg. 850
    2 2_sar_1.tif 2_1.tif (类别  sar_path  optical_path)


